            <title>[LUCENE-3680] exception consistency in o.a.l.store</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3680</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;just some minor improvements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;always use EOFException when its eof&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;always include the inputstream too so we know filename etc&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;use FileNotFoundException consistently in CFS when a sub-file is not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
